# Surge RULE-SET (Douyin / ByteDance CN) - Force US
# Target Policy: US
# Purpose:
# - Force Douyin (抖音) and ByteDance CN ecosystem traffic to go through policy "US".
# - This makes Douyin services see your US node egress/public IP (what people call "modify IP").
#
# Usage (Surge):
#   [Rule]
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/douyin_proxy.list,US
#
# Notes:
# - Place this RULE-SET ABOVE: GEOIP,MY / china.list / GEOIP,CN
# - If any Douyin traffic still goes DIRECT, add missing SNI/hosts here.

# -----------------------
# Douyin core
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,douyin.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,iesdouyin.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,douyinpic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,douyinstatic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,douyincdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,douyinliving.com

# -----------------------
# ByteDance app platform (VERY important)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,snssdk.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,amemv.com

# -----------------------
# ByteDance core / common APIs
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bytedance.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,byted.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,byteimg.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bytecdn.cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bytegoofy.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bytegecko.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bytescm.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bytetcc.com

DOMAIN-SUFFIX,zijieapi.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,zijieimg.com

# Shared content family often used by Douyin
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,toutiao.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ixigua.com

# -----------------------
# Volcengine / ByteDance Cloud (backend/CDN commonly appears)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,volcengine.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,volces.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,volccdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,volccdn1.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,volccdn2.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,volccdn3.com

# -----------------------
# IES CDN domains frequently seen in ByteDance apps
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,iescdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,iesimg.com